channel.title: Weird error
channel.description:
So, it started out small and i though no biggie. on very few accounts, it would say "account already logged in, please wait 60 seconds." And if it did that, you could never get on the acc again. but it was small. just 2-3 days ago, it started doing it to EVERY SINGLE ACCOUNT. now, no one can get on. at the same time the error occured to every account, I was working on custom weapons. i made a weapon (axe) in a 3d program called blender. then i scripted it, and made it a .obj file so the game would accept it, and added it to the models in my client. then i had to proporly add it in the server. these are the files i edited.
Client.java item.java item.cfg itemhandeler.
thats it.
5 minutes ago, i deleted all of it. took away the things i added in all the files. still the error. so im wondeering has this happened to ANYONE before? if so, i would gladly accept and educated guess's.
thanks.
